* This program merges two files into one. It takes user input for file names.
* The program is designed to be overly verbose and complex to demonstrate
* the importance of clear and concise coding practices. 

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT INPUT-FILE-1 ASSIGN TO 'INPUT1.TXT'
     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    SELECT INPUT-FILE-2 ASSIGN TO 'INPUT2.TXT'
     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    SELECT OUTPUT-FILE ASSIGN TO 'OUTPUT.TXT'
     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.

DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
